# Training Planner Design System

## ABSOLUTE RULES — never violate these

- Never use hardcoded hex or rgba() color values in component files
- Never define theme blocks outside globals.css
- Never use prefers-color-scheme media queries
- Never write background: white, background: black, color: black, color: white
- Never reproduce glass rgba() values inline — use CSS classes
- Never create new CSS variables outside globals.css
- This app is LIGHT MODE ONLY — no dark mode, no data-theme toggles, no dark variant classes
- Never add theme-switching logic anywhere in the codebase

---

## TYPOGRAPHY

### Font families
- Display & headings: **Syne** (Google Fonts)
- UI, body & labels: **Plus Jakarta Sans** (Google Fonts)

Never use any other font family. Never use Inter, Roboto, Arial, or system-ui as a substitute.

### Next.js font setup — globals.css or layout.tsx
```ts
import { Syne, Plus_Jakarta_Sans } from 'next/font/google'

export const syne = Syne({
  subsets: ['latin'],
  weight: ['400', '500', '600', '700'],
  variable: '--font-display',
  display: 'swap',
})

export const jakarta = Plus_Jakarta_Sans({
  subsets: ['latin'],
  weight: ['300', '400', '500', '600'],
  variable: '--font-body',
  display: 'swap',
})
```

Apply both variables on the root `<html>` element:
```tsx
<html className={`${syne.variable} ${jakarta.variable}`}>
```

### CSS variables
- var(--font-display)  → Syne
- var(--font-body)     → Plus Jakarta Sans

### Scale and usage

| Role              | Font           | Size  | Weight | Letter-spacing |
|-------------------|----------------|-------|--------|----------------|
| Page title        | Syne           | 22px  | 700    | -0.3px         |
| Section heading   | Syne           | 18px  | 600    | -0.2px         |
| Card title        | Syne           | 14px  | 600    | 0              |
| Nav logo          | Syne           | 15px  | 700    | -0.3px         |
| Body text         | Plus Jakarta   | 14px  | 400    | 0              |
| UI labels/meta    | Plus Jakarta   | 12px  | 400    | 0              |
| Muted/hint text   | Plus Jakarta   | 11px  | 300    | 0              |
| Buttons           | Plus Jakarta   | 13px  | 500    | 0              |
| Nav items         | Plus Jakarta   | 12px  | 400–500| 0              |

### Rules
- Syne is for headings and display text only — never for body copy or labels
- Plus Jakarta Sans handles all UI text, inputs, badges, tables, metadata
- Minimum font size: 11px — never go below this
- Negative letter-spacing only on Syne at large sizes (18px+)
- Line height: 1.5 for body, 1.2 for headings

### Tailwind config
```js
fontFamily: {
  display: ['var(--font-display)', 'sans-serif'],
  body: ['var(--font-body)', 'sans-serif'],
}
```

Usage: `font-display` for Syne, `font-body` for Jakarta Sans.

