## GRADIENT LIBRARY — three defined gradients only

### Primary — header navigation, primary CTAs
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D5A46 0%, #1DBF8A 45%, #6385FF 100%)
  Use for: app header bar, primary call-to-action buttons

### Aurora — hero cards, featured elements
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1DBF8A 0%, #6385FF 100%)
  Use for: hero stat cards, featured plan accents, avatar backgrounds

### Soft — background blobs, decorative areas
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #34c99a 0%, #a8f0da 100%)
  Use for: background blob elements, decorative sections

Never create new gradients outside these three.
Never use gradients inline in component files — reference CSS variables only.

