## NAVIGATION STRUCTURE

Top navigation bar using Primary gradient. Four items:

1. Plans       — main list of training plans
2. Phases      — phase library (cross-plan view)
3. Exercises   — exercise library
4. Competitors — competitor profiles and tracking

No sidebar. No dashboard. Entry point is always Plans list.
Breadcrumb navigation used for drill-down: Plans › Plan name › Phase name

