## SURFACE HIERARCHY — light mode only

Layer 0 — Page background
  var(--color-base) → #EAF7F2 mint mist
  Soft gradient blobs animate on top using Soft gradient

Layer 1 — Glass panels, main content areas
  class: glass-panel
  rgba(255,255,255,0.72) frosted white, blur(12px)
  border: rgba(255,255,255,0.90) — bright white border for frosted effect

Layer 2 — Cards inside panels, inputs
  rgba(255,255,255,0.86)
  Whiter than panel to create depth

Layer 3 — Elevated elements, dropdowns, tooltips, popovers
  rgba(255,255,255,0.95) or var(--color-surface-raised)
  Most opaque layer

Layer 4 — Navigation header
  Primary gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D5A46 0%, #1DBF8A 45%, #6385FF 100%)
  Always sits at top, always full width

