## TEXT CONTRAST — WCAG AA minimum 4.5:1

- Headings: var(--color-text-primary) → #111827
- Section titles: var(--color-accent-dark) → #0D5A46
- Body: var(--color-text-secondary) → #374151
- Muted: var(--color-text-muted) → #6B7280
- Accent: var(--color-text-accent) → #0A7A52

Never:
- White or near-white text on light backgrounds
- rgba(255,255,255,0.X) as text color outside the nav header
- Light gray above #9CA3AF as body text

