## INTERACTIVE STATES

Active nav item (on gradient header):
  background rgba(255,255,255,0.18), color #ffffff, font-weight 500
  backdrop-filter blur(8px), border 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25)

Inactive nav hover (on gradient header):
  background rgba(255,255,255,0.10), color rgba(255,255,255,0.90)

Primary button:
  background: Primary gradient, color #ffffff
  box-shadow: var(--cta-shadow)
  hover: var(--btn-primary-hover-bg), var(--cta-shadow-hover)

Ghost button:
  background: var(--color-accent-muted)
  border: var(--color-border)
  color: var(--color-accent-dark)
  hover: var(--btn-ghost-hover-bg), var(--btn-ghost-hover-border)

