## GLASSMORPHISM REQUIREMENTS

- Background blobs MUST be present — they provide color context behind the frosted glass
- Every glass surface MUST have: semi-transparent background, backdrop-filter blur(), -webkit-backdrop-filter blur(), white-tinted border, subtle box-shadow
- Glass opacity is higher than previous system (0.72 vs 0.45) — this is intentional for the frosted style
- Glass surfaces MUST NOT have: fully transparent background, fully opaque background, overflow:hidden on parent clipping blur, transform or filter on parent breaking backdrop-filter

