## FORBIDDEN PATTERNS — never generate these

- color: #111827 inline              → use var(--color-text-primary)
- color: #374151 inline              → use var(--color-text-secondary)
- color: #6B7280 inline              → use var(--color-text-muted)
- color: #1DBF8A inline              → use var(--color-accent)
- color: #0D5A46 inline              → use var(--color-accent-dark)
- background: rgba(29,191,138,...) inline → use CSS variable
- background: rgba(255,255,255,...) inline → use glass-panel class
- background: white                  → use var(--color-surface-raised)
- color: white outside nav header    → use var(--color-text-primary)
- prefers-color-scheme               → never, app is light-only
- [data-theme="dark"]                → fully removed
- data-theme attribute anywhere      → fully removed
- Dark mode Tailwind variants (dark:) → fully removed
- new gradient values not in library → use only the three defined gradients
- font-family: Inter, Roboto, Arial, system-ui → use var(--font-display) or var(--font-body)
- Syne on body text or labels              → Syne is display/headings only
- font-size below 11px                     → minimum is 11px

